      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Biscuit base",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Heat the oven to 160°C fan. Blitz the {{digestive-biscuit}} to fine crumbs (or crush in a bag with a rolling pin). Mix with the melted {{unsalted-butter}}. Press evenly into a 23 cm tin, pushing up the sides 2 cm. Bake for 10 minutes to set. Cool while you make the filling.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Filling, bake low",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Whisk the {{condensed-milk}} with the {{egg-yolks}} until smooth. Whisk in the zest and juice of the {{lime}}; the mixture will thicken visibly as the acid hits the milk. Pour into the cooled base. Bake for 15 minutes; the edges should be set, the centre should wobble slightly. Cool fully, then chill at least 4 hours, or overnight.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Whipped cream top",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Whip the {{double-cream}} with the {{icing-sugar}} to soft peaks. Spoon or pipe over the chilled pie. Serve with a little extra lime zest on top.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
